title: New Team Looking for ADC

embed.description: Oceanic Gaming is home to Rusted World and Oceanic ARK!

body:
Hey guys and gals!
Fyre here looking to set up a new Oceanic Gaming Network team, with our roster slowly filling we are looking for an ADC to complete our first team!
We would love to have anyone join so feel free to jump to our forums, or even join our discord and have a chat with myself or Mary.

Discord : https://discord.gg/B5UcxFX 

Don't be afraid to come on in and ask any question :)

replies.body: Hey man, no stress about ranks hey just come on and have a chat :)
no such thing my friend, we all are here to learn and grow :)
